一諗，<br />\n郁啲就扣帽係咪等於割蓆？<br />\n你叫嘅口號，同自己實際做出嚟嘅嘢，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">有冇背道而馳</span></strong></span>？<br />\n係咪不知不覺，走緊雨革條舊路？<br />\n<br />\n我唔希望呢個Post沉，<br />\n但更加唔想又炒起一場場嘅批鬥。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>此風不可長</strong></span></span>。<br />\n你覺得啱聽嘅，推，<br />\n唔啱聽嘅，即管負皮。<br />\n但負皮之前，希望你不服來辯。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">用理據質疑我，用邏輯反駁我。</span></strong></span><br />\n我衰撚咗，我接受你嘅負皮同恥笑。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，我係擺明嚟帶風向嘅。<br />\n來生不做中國人，<br />\n但今生更不做<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">醜陋的中國人</span></strong></span>。<br />\n連登仔，希望你地都一樣。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:53:54.000Z","msg":"贏咗再講"},{"pid":"72eb792e3b39757268dde409bb3d555ca84bf273","tid":1384083,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:54:40.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多<br />\n大家加油<br />\n勿忘初衷"},{"pid":"5c8867c3195ca690832326ac17093c6e67401f02","tid":1384083,"uid":234089,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:55:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">起完底知咩料！唔洗覆 block得</span></span>"},{"pid":"045ae7c10dfb1cb2300cbbcb6a4d7634a25a3422","tid":1384083,"uid":126042,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"已經有幾個連衛兵睇都唔睇就負皮你"},{"pid":"62f9cd97464b915c767d36a55b4a3306186ebf31","tid":1384083,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:00:56.000Z","msg":"癈青根本想玩到一國兩制即刻結束，變成一國一制，係共產黨嘅fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fef5c65d9a49ba56026c799c9665876d7bd8ee","tid":1384083,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:03:31.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;扣帽子&rdquo;3字就係共產黨詞彙，樓主用少d好"},{"pid":"d3b7b2a1fe344f9640a1dab57d3d57a83accf61e","tid":1384083,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":